## How to Use RSS Feeds

RSS feeds allow you to stay updated with new content without visiting the site directly. Here are some popular RSS readers:

- **Web-based**: [Feedly](https://feedly.com/), [Inoreader](https://www.inoreader.com/), [The Old Reader](https://theoldreader.com/)
- **Desktop**: [NetNewsWire](https://netnewswire.com/) (Mac), [FreshRSS](https://freshrss.org/) (Self-hosted)
- **Mobile**: [Reeder](https://reederapp.com/) (iOS), [Read You](https://github.com/Ashinch/ReadYou) (Android)

Simply copy one of the feed URLs above and add it to your RSS reader application.

